I'm in Summerville. I lived in Lexington 2 yrs ago.<<<

Are you familiar with School's Out Support? www.schoolsoutsupport.org

We hosted the last two (and first two) unschooling conferences!

Join us; we're statewide. And you might want to start a local , maybe
Greater Charleston, unschooling group----there are SEVERAL unschoolers in the Low
Country.

~Kelly
